sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Operator as Operator
    participant Dashboard as Incident Workspace
    participant API as sre_agent API v1
    participant Graph as LangGraph Runtime
    participant Tools as MCP Tool Servers
    participant Store as Backend DB / Redis

    Operator->>Dashboard: Send follow-up message
    Dashboard->>API: POST /api/v1/incidents/{id}/message
    API->>Store: Persist message and queue investigation turn
    API->>Graph: Trigger new incident investigation turn
    Graph->>Tools: Gather logs, metrics, runbooks, GitHub evidence
    Tools-->>Graph: Evidence payloads
    Graph->>Store: Write timeline events and updated summary
    Graph-->>API: Return structured investigation result
    API-->>Dashboard: Updated transcript and incident status
